<view class="container">
  <view class="page-title">联系客服</view>

  <view class="service-box">
    <view class="service-item" bindtap="makeCall">
      <view class="service-left">
        <text class="service-icon">📞</text>
        <text class="service-title">客服电话</text>
      </view>
      <text class="service-value">400-888-9999</text>
    </view>

    <view class="service-item" bindtap="openChat">
      <view class="service-left">
        <text class="service-icon">💬</text>
        <text class="service-title">在线客服</text>
      </view>
      <text class="service-arrow">></text>
    </view>

    <view class="service-item">
      <view class="service-left">
        <text class="service-icon">🕒</text>
        <text class="service-title">工作时间</text>
      </view>
      <text class="service-value">9:00-21:00</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="service-desc">
    如遇订单、商品、售后等问题，可通过以上方式联系我们，我们将尽快为您处理。
  </view>
</view>